ry prerequisite that makes the parent sequence executable.\n    \u003c/description\u003e\n    \u003cacceptance\u003e\n1. A new design/inventory doc under `docs/helix/02-design/` references ADR-008 and `fizeau-cd9af16b` and buckets every root-level `.go` file into public facade, public compatibility alias/shim, or internal-owner categories.\u0026#xA;2. The doc lists the in-repo `github.com/easel/fizeau` consumers, including `agentcli/`, `cmd/bench/`, `cmd/fiz/`, and root black-box tests, and states why parent AC #1 (zero root `.go` files) is incompatible with ADR-008 without a replacement public package.\u0026#xA;3. The doc names the follow-on extraction slices in execution order and the target internal packages for each slice.\u0026#xA;4. `go test ./agentcli -run \u0026#39;TestCLIInternalImportBoundaryAllowlist|TestCLIBoundaryForbiddenInternalImports|TestCLIBoundaryForbiddenSymbols\u0026#39; -count=1` passes.\u0026#xA;5. `go test ./... -count=1` passes.\u0026#xA;6. `lefthook run pre-commit` passes.\n    \u003c/acceptance\u003e\n    \u003clabels\u003ephase:design, area:repo-structure, kind:refactor, spec:ADR-008\u003c/labels\u003e\n    \u003cmetadata parent=\"fizeau-cd9af16b\" spec-id=\"ADR-008\" base-rev=\"4bc767a16a668dfe35d198580b0107b82c27f19f\" bundle=\".ddx/executions/20260515T091924-3e2a59e4\"/\u003e\n  \u003c/bead\u003e\n  \u003cgoverning\u003e\n    \u003cref id=\"ADR-008\" path=\"docs/helix/02-design/adr/ADR-008-service-package-and-transcript-boundaries.md\"\u003eADR-008: Service Package and Transcript Boundaries\u003c/ref\u003e\n  \u003c/governing\u003e\n\u003c/execute-bead\u003e\n","metadata":{"DDX_MODE":"bead_execution","attempt_id":"20260515T091924-3e2a59e4","base_rev":"4bc767a16a668dfe35d198580b0107b82c27f19f","bead_id":"fizeau-0247682e","bundle_path":".ddx/executions/20260515T091924-3e2a59e4","correlation_id":"fizeau-0247682e:20260515T091924-3e2a59e4","prompt_file":".ddx/executions/20260515T091924-3e2a59e4/prompt.md","prompt_sha":"4737f561beb97c57607fb